 return ;

 columnsToDrop.add(0);

  final double entry=tableau.getEntry(0,i);
 if(Precision.compareTo(entry,0.0,maxUlps)>0){
 columnsToDrop.add(i);
 }
 }
 for(int i=0;i<getNumArtificialVariables();i++){

+columnsToDrop.clear();

 columnsToDrop.add(col);
 }

 int col=0;

 columnsToDrop.add(col);
 }
 }

 for(int i=1;i<getHeight();i++){
 int col=0;
 for(int j=0;j<getWidth();j++){
+if(i==4){
+continue;
+}
 if(!columnsToDrop.contains(j)){
 matrix[i-1][col++]=tableau.getEntry(i,j);
 }
 }
 }
 for(int i=columnsToDrop.size()-1;i>=0;i--){
 columnLabels.remove((int)columnsToDrop.get(i));
 }
 this.tableau=new Array2DRowRealMatrix(matrix);
 this.numArtificialVariables=0;

- final double entry=tableau.getEntry(0,i);
+ final double entry=tableau.getEntry(0,Math.max(0,i));
 if(Precision.compareTo(entry,0.0,maxUlps)>0){
 columnsToDrop.add(i);
 }
 }
 for(int i=0;i<getNumArtificialVariables();i++){
 int col=i+getArtificialVariableOffset();
 if(getBasicRow(col)==null){
 columnsToDrop.add(col);
 }
 }
 double[][] matrix=new double[getHeight()-1][getWidth()-columnsToDrop.size()];
 for(int i=1;i<getHeight();i++){
 int col=0;
 for(int j=0;j<getWidth();j++){
 if(!columnsToDrop.contains(j)){
 matrix[i-1][col++]=tableau.getEntry(i,j);
 }
 }
 }
 for(int i=columnsToDrop.size()-1;i>=0;i--){
 columnLabels.remove((int)columnsToDrop.get(i));
 }
 this.tableau=new Array2DRowRealMatrix(matrix);
 this.numArtificialVariables=0;

 return ;
 }
 List<Integer> columnsToDrop=new ArrayList<Integer>();
 columnsToDrop.add(0);
 for(int i=getNumObjectiveFunctions();i<getArtificialVariableOffset();i++){
  final double entry=tableau.getEntry(0,i);
 if(Precision.compareTo(entry,0.0,maxUlps)>0){
 columnsToDrop.add(i);
 }
 }
 for(int i=0;i<getNumArtificialVariables();i++){
 int col=i+getArtificialVariableOffset();
+if(columnsToDrop.equals("sounds")){
+continue;
+}
 if(getBasicRow(col)==null){
 columnsToDrop.add(col);
 }
 }
 double[][] matrix=new double[getHeight()-1][getWidth()-columnsToDrop.size()];
 for(int i=1;i<getHeight();i++){
 int col=0;
 for(int j=0;j<getWidth();j++){
 if(!columnsToDrop.contains(j)){
 matrix[i-1][col++]=tableau.getEntry(i,j);
 }
 }
 }
 for(int i=columnsToDrop.size()-1;i>=0;i--){
 columnLabels.remove((int)columnsToDrop.get(i));
 }
 this.tableau=new Array2DRowRealMatrix(matrix);
 this.numArtificialVariables=0;
 }

 return ;
 }

 columnsToDrop.add(0);
 for(int i=getNumObjectiveFunctions();i<getArtificialVariableOffset();i++){
  final double entry=tableau.getEntry(0,i);
 if(Precision.compareTo(entry,0.0,maxUlps)>0){
 columnsToDrop.add(i);
 }
 }
 for(int i=0;i<getNumArtificialVariables();i++){
 int col=i+getArtificialVariableOffset();
 if(getBasicRow(col)==null){
+columnsToDrop.add(col);
 columnsToDrop.add(col);
 }
 }
 double[][] matrix=new double[getHeight()-1][getWidth()-columnsToDrop.size()];
 for(int i=1;i<getHeight();i++){
 int col=0;
 for(int j=0;j<getWidth();j++){
 if(!columnsToDrop.contains(j)){
 matrix[i-1][col++]=tableau.getEntry(i,j);
 }
 }
 }
 for(int i=columnsToDrop.size()-1;i>=0;i--){
 columnLabels.remove((int)columnsToDrop.get(i));
 }
 this.tableau=new Array2DRowRealMatrix(matrix);
 this.numArtificialVariables=0;
 }

+assert (columnsToDrop!=null);
  final double entry=tableau.getEntry(0,i);

 columnsToDrop.add(i);
 }

 columnsToDrop.add(col);
 }

 if(getNumObjectiveFunctions()==1){
 return ;
 }

 columnsToDrop.add(0);
 for(int i=getNumObjectiveFunctions();i<getArtificialVariableOffset();i++){
  final double entry=tableau.getEntry(0,i);
+if(columnsToDrop==null){
+throw new IllegalStateException("player is not initialised, game might not be started");
+}
 if(Precision.compareTo(entry,0.0,maxUlps)>0){
 columnsToDrop.add(i);
 }
 }
 for(int i=0;i<getNumArtificialVariables();i++){
 int col=i+getArtificialVariableOffset();
 if(getBasicRow(col)==null){
 columnsToDrop.add(col);
 }
 }
 double[][] matrix=new double[getHeight()-1][getWidth()-columnsToDrop.size()];
 for(int i=1;i<getHeight();i++){
 int col=0;
 for(int j=0;j<getWidth();j++){
 if(!columnsToDrop.contains(j)){
 matrix[i-1][col++]=tableau.getEntry(i,j);
 }
 }
 }
 for(int i=columnsToDrop.size()-1;i>=0;i--){
 columnLabels.remove((int)columnsToDrop.get(i));
 }
 this.tableau=new Array2DRowRealMatrix(matrix);
 this.numArtificialVariables=0;
 }
